text: On the heels of reports that Jessica Simpson is pregnant with her third child, RadarOnline.com has obtained photographs of the songstress sporting what appears to be a baby bump. And despite the mother-of-two recently denying being with child, these new images only add more fuel to the speculation. Click through the gallery and let us know what you think!
title: Jessica Simpson Fuels Pregnancy Rumors In Shocking New Photos
